95806430-ca61-11eb-a3a8-7f87635b1dbc.content: [{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"text":"Calculate the linear regression of power co-ef based on Avg wind speed. Regression-based on 80 meter height wind speed and temp. ","bold":true}]},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"text":"Now let us predict the power co-ef based on the latest temperature and windspeed data from the weather service","bold":true}]}]

95806430-ca61-11eb-a3a8-7f87635b1dbc.name: Block
95806430-ca61-11eb-a3a8-7f87635b1dbc.content:
"EXECUTE FUNCTION prediction
( INPUT_TABLE_NAMES => INPUT_TABLES(
    (SELECT "Avg_Wind_Speed___80m_[m.s]"  as speed, "Temperature___80m_[deg_C]" as temp, "Mean_Power_Law_Coef_[2.80m]" as power_coef_80 
       FROM NRELWindmill ORDER BY DOY),
    (SELECT LON, LAT, TIMESTAMP(streaming_weatherview.date1), windspeed as speed, temp FROM streaming_weatherview 
         WHERE (date1 >= DATEADD('MINUTE', -30, now())) )
    ),
OUTPUT_TABLE_NAMES => OUTPUT_TABLES('ki_home.power_predict') )"

95806430-ca61-11eb-a3a8-7f87635b1dbc.name: Block
95806430-ca61-11eb-a3a8-7f87635b1dbc.content: "SELECT id1 as LON, id2 as LAT, datetime(id3) as DATE_TIME, var1 as windspeed, var2 as temp, predict_float as predicted_power_coef\n FROM ki_home.power_predict\n ORDER BY DATE_TIME DESC"

95806430-ca61-11eb-a3a8-7f87635b1dbc.name: Block
95806430-ca61-11eb-a3a8-7f87635b1dbc.content:
"EXECUTE FUNCTION prediction3
( INPUT_TABLE_NAMES => INPUT_TABLES(
    (SELECT "Avg_Wind_Speed___80m_[m.s]"  as speed, "Temperature___80m_[deg_C]" s temp, "Mean_Power_Law_Coef_[2.80m]" as power_coef_80 FROM NRELWindmill WHERE DOY in (135, 136)),
    (SELECT "Avg_Wind_Speed___50m_[m.s]"  as speed, "Temperature___50m_[deg_C]" as temp FROM NRELWindmill WHERE DOY in (135, 136)) ),
OUTPUT_TABLE_NAMES => OUTPUT_TABLES('ki_home.multi_predict') )"

95806430-ca61-11eb-a3a8-7f87635b1dbc.name: Block
95806430-ca61-11eb-a3a8-7f87635b1dbc.content:
"SELECT 50  "height_in_meter" , var1 as speed, SUM(ABS(predict_float)) as total_power_cef_predicted 
FROM ki_home.multi_predict 
GROUP BY speed
LIMIT 10"

95806430-ca61-11eb-a3a8-7f87635b1dbc.name: Block
95806430-ca61-11eb-a3a8-7f87635b1dbc.content: [{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"text":"Now predict what would be power coeff, if the windmill height was changed to 50 meter","bold":true}]}]

95806430-ca61-11eb-a3a8-7f87635b1dbc.name: Block
95806430-ca61-11eb-a3a8-7f87635b1dbc.content:
"SELECT id1 as LON, id2 as LAT,  datetime(id3) as DATE_TIME, var1 as windspeed, var2 as temp, predict_float as predicted_power_coef, TO_CHAR(datetime(id3), 'HH24:MI') as t, ABS(predict_float) as predict_power
FROM TABLE(prediction
( INPUT_TABLE_NAMES => INPUT_TABLES(
    (SELECT "Avg_Wind_Speed___80m_[m.s]"  as speed, "Temperature___80m_[deg_C]" as temp, "Mean_Power_Law_Coef_[2.80m]" as power_coef_80 FROM NRELWindmill ORDER BY DOY DESC LIMIT 100000),
    (SELECT LON, LAT, TIMESTAMP(streaming_weatherview.date1), windspeed as speed, temp 
         FROM streaming_weatherview WHERE GEODIST(-105.2347,39.9106, LON, LAT) < 5000)
    ) ))
 WHERE datetime(id3) >= DATEADD('MINUTE', -40, now())  
ORDER BY DATE_TIME ASC"

95806430-ca61-11eb-a3a8-7f87635b1dbc.name: Block
95806430-ca61-11eb-a3a8-7f87635b1dbc.content:
"CREATE OR REPLACE MATERIALIZED VIEW power_view AS
 SELECT id1 as LON, id2 as LAT, ROUND(MAX(predict_float*100)) as predicted_power_coef
 FROM ki_home.power_predict
 GROUP BY LON, LAT
 "

95c13dc0-ca61-11eb-a3a8-7f87635b1dbc.content:
"CREATE OR REPLACE MATERIALIZED VIEW streaming_weatherview 
REFRESH ON QUERY
AS
SELECT DECIMAL(SPLIT (REPLACE(REPLACE( REPLACE(coord, '{"lon":', '') , '"lat":',''), '}', '') , ',', 1)) as LON, 
       DECIMAL(SPLIT (REPLACE(REPLACE( REPLACE(coord, '{"lon":', '') , '"lat":',''), '}', '') , ',', 2)) as LAT,  
       DECIMAL( SPLIT (REPLACE(main, '{"temp":', ''), ',', 1  ) ) as temp,
        DECIMAL( SPLIT (REPLACE(wind, '{"speed":', ''), ',', 1  ) ) as windspeed,
         date as date1, name, id
FROM streaming_weather"
